<h1>Ranger</h1>

<h5>Alignment</h5>
<p>
	Any.
</p>

<h5>Hit Die</h5>
<p>
	d8.
</p>

<h4>Class Skills</h4>
<p>
	The ranger=E2=80=99s class skills (and the key ability for each skill) are=
 <a href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/skills/climb.htm">Climb</a> (Str), <=
a href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/skills/concentration.htm">Concentratio=
n</a> (Con), <a href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/skills/craft.htm">Craft<=
/a> (Int), <a href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/skills/handleAnimal.htm">H=
andle Animal</a> (Cha), <a href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/skills/heal.h=
tm">Heal</a> (Wis), <a href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/skills/hide.htm">=
Hide</a> (Dex), <a href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/skills/jump.htm">Jump=
</a> (Str), <a href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/skills/knowledge.htm">Kno=
wledge</a> (dungeoneering) (Int), <a href=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/ski=
lls/knowledge.htm">Knowledge</a> (geography) (Int), <a href=3D"https://www.=
d20srd.org/srd/skills/knowledge.htm">Knowledge</a> (nature) (Int), <a href=
=3D"https://www.d20srd.org/srd/skills/listen.htm">Listen</a> (Wis), <a href=
