e</a> (Dex).
</p>

<h5>Skill Points at 1st Level</h5>
<p>
	(6 + Int modifier) =C3=974.
</p>

<h5>Skill Points at Each Additional Level</h5>
<p>
	6 + Int modifier.
</p>

